text: Alexandra Schilling (born 9 November 1981) is a German female water polo player. She was part of the Germany women's national water polo team at the 2009 Women's Water Polo World League, and 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * dutch-jantien-cabout-fights-for-the- ball-with-german alexandra schilling Getty Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:German water polo players
